Importing VitalDBR
```{r}
library(devtools)
install_github('legendenomgeorg/VitalDBR/VitalDBR')
library(VitalDBR)
```

Loading in data
```{r}
df <- load_case('Primus/AWP', 1)

```

```{r}
plot(df)
```
```{r}
tisek<- df[100000:(100000+(10*62.5))] #  10 sekunder fra 10000 (cirka 625 observationer)
plot(tisek, type='l')
```
